==English==
===Noun===
'''hangnail'''
# a loose narrow strip of skin near the base of a fingernail or toenail.  Known to be quite painful.  The term 'hangnail' is misleading as a hangnail is not an actual piece of nail.  It's dead dried skin not nail which is made up of mostly calcium and a fibrous protein, known as Keratin.

